      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       wrt-rec-cpv-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione record                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-rec-cpv-000      thru cmp-rec-cpv-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
