                                               rf-cpv                 .
       wrt-rec-cpv-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Riscrittura record righe [cpv]                            *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       rew-rec-cpv-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Cancellazione preventiva delle righe            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Start su righe corpo                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      1                    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se start non valida : a scrittura       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to rew-rec-cpv-500.
       rew-rec-cpv-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura sequenziale righe corpo             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se at end : a scrittura righe           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to rew-rec-cpv-400.
       rew-rec-cpv-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Delete record file righe [cpv]              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   del-rec-cpv-000      thru del-rec-cpv-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo a lettura riga corpo successiva     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     rew-rec-cpv-100.
       rew-rec-cpv-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura delle righe                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione progressivo righe           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-cix-ctr-prg
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Start su righe corpo                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      1                    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se start non valida : uscita            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to rew-rec-cpv-999.
       rew-rec-cpv-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura sequenziale righe corpo             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se at end : uscita                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to rew-rec-cpv-999.
       rew-rec-cpv-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento progressivo righe                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       00100                to   w-cix-ctr-prg          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Write record [cpv]                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   wrt-rec-cpv-000      thru wrt-rec-cpv-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo a lettura riga corpo successiva     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     rew-rec-cpv-500.
       rew-rec-cpv-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Cancellazione record righe [cpv]                          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       del-rec-cpv-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione chiave primaria                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      01                   to   rf-cpv-tip-rec         .
           move      w-tes-cod-cpv        to   rf-cpv-cod-cpv         .
           move      w-rig-num-pro (2)    to   rf-cpv-num-pro         .
