           if        w-fnd-rlt-pro-alf    =    w-rig-alf-pro (1)
                     move  w-cat-rig-cur  to   w-fnd-rlt-pro-num
                     move  "#"            to   w-fnd-rlt-pro-flg
                     go to fnd-rlt-pro-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo                                         *
